item.title: Java Overview
item.description:
Welcome to the Java Overview page. Here you will find key information about what Java is, why you might want to use it, and how it can benefit your projects.

What is Java?

Java is a widely-used, high-level programming language known for its simplicity, portability, and performance. It allows developers to write code once and run it anywhere, thanks to the Java Virtual Machine (JVM). Java has been a staple of enterprise-level applications and Android development for decades.
